reviewText: So freaking funny!!! These shows are a great way to learn something new and have lots of laughs! !!
What is not to like about Carson?!  Makes me wish Queer Eye was still on.

I was prepared for some dissapointment with this DVD, needless to say I did not get it. ^_^ This is exactly what Carson fans want, I have watched it 4 times in less than 24 hours. Obsessive as that may sound. This is so great! I only hope the rest of the QE DVDs are as good.
Well, I'm absolutely obsessed with Queer Eye, so naturally I had to buy this.  However, the reason I gave it five stars, other than my obsession, is the outtakes.  I really love the outtakes!
